items.title: He Is Alive
items.label: Not On Label
items.comments: Stored in plastic outer sleeve, and sleeve city inner. Cover has a bit of ring wear and 2 inch rectangular spot that looks like a sticker removal impression. Label in great shape and vinyl has superficial hairs that minimally affect play. Some light ticks in portions of the record, and it jumps around from VG, VG+ to G+. items.title: Those Darlins
items.label: Oh Wow Dang Records
items.comments: Stored in plastic outer sleeve, and sleeve city inner. Vinyl looks unplayed and sounds great. Sleeve/cover has some light creasing and corner wear, but really nice overall (happy to provide pics). Comes with OIS but no CD.

items.title: Paul's Boutique
items.label: Beastie Boys Records
items.comments: Stored in plastic outer sleeve, and mofi inner. Jacket is in pretty good condition, just has corner/edge wear & a little creasing (happy to provide pics or audio sample). Media is a little tough to grade, as side B toggles between VG & VG+, while side A starts out G+ but after the first 2 or 3 songs switches to VG (has quite a few surface hairs on both sides). Comes with OIS and has gray bar code sticker attached to the back cover.

items.title: Butthole Surfers
items.label: Alternative Tentacles
items.comments: Stored in plastic outer sleeve, and sleeve city inner. Media has some surface marks, but plays strong (heard one pop during play and some noise between tracks). Front cover looks really nice, and the back is good but has a little light creasing and a 2 inch thin line (next to the head). Little corner wear and crunch as well, but overall very nice (happy to provide pics).

items.title: Question In The Form Of An Answer
items.label: OM Records
items.comments: Stored in plastic outer sleeve, and sleeve city inners. Media has a lot superficial hairs that are seen under bright light. Plays closer to VG+, but knocking this down a bit because of the visual grade (heard very little surface noise - occasional pop mostly in the quiet parts). Sleeve still in shrink, but receding a bit at opening and has a fair amount of corner wear, 2 inch+ seam split at the top & large corner clip (maybe G+, but I think VG is accurate). Great player copy
